ly slow inertial range separations have\na non self-similar probability distribution function.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Nov 2014 17:38:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 18 Feb 2015 17:59:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-19"}
